Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.17,0:00:08.27,Default,Nakao,0,0,0,,{\i1}I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.27,0:00:11.55,Default,Girl1,0,0,0,,I heard Nakao \Nwas hit by a boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.55,0:00:14.68,Default,Girl2,0,0,0,,So leaving Yomiyama \Ndoesn't negate the curse?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.68,0:00:16.03,Default,Girl1,0,0,0,,I guess not.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.03,0:00:19.07,Default,Girl2,0,0,0,,Sheesh... So we can't escape it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.07,0:00:20.48,Default,Girl2,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.07,0:00:24.29,Default,Girl1,0,0,0,,Hey... are you still \Ngoing on the class trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.29,0:00:26.29,Default,Girl2,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.29,0:00:30.34,Default,Girl2,0,0,0,,Why would we go on a class trip the summer when it happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.59,0:00:34.34,Default,Girl2,0,0,0,,We should just stay \Nlocked up at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.34,0:00:35.43,Default,Girl1,0,0,0,,I suppose so.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.84,0:00:40.52,Default,Girl2,0,0,0,,But... why is this \Nhappening to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.52,0:00:42.04,Default,Girl2,0,0,0,,It's so unfair.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.04,0:00:43.10,Default,Girl1,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.10,0:00:47.72,Default,Girl1,0,0,0,,If only that transfer student \Nhadn't spoken to Misaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.52,0:00:49.21,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,{\i1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.80,0:00:52.53,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,{\i1}I protected them...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.92,0:00:56.49,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,{\i1}I left it for them...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.60,0:00:59.01,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,{\i1}...in the classroom.
